---
// Standalone landing page - no standard header/footer
import '../../styles/global.css'
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Get Your Business on ChatGPT | Rank4AI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Get your business recommended by ChatGPT. Free AI Search Visibility Audit from Rank4AI.">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <link rel="icon" href="/logo.png">
</head>
<body class="bg-white min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-[600px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
    <img src="/logo.png" alt="Rank4AI" class="h-8 mx-auto mb-12 opacity-60">

    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4">UK AI Search Agency</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-teal leading-tight mb-6">Get Your Business Recommended by ChatGPT</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">When someone asks ChatGPT to recommend a business like yours, do you appear?</p>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">We test your visibility across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI. You get a detailed report showing exactly where you stand.</p>

    <div class="bg-off-white rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 text-left">
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-teal mb-4 text-center">Get Your Free AI Search Visibility Audit</h2>
      <form action="https://formsubmit.co/info@rank4ai.co.uk" method="POST" class="space-y-4"><input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="PPC Lead from Rank4AI"><input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false"><input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your name" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg text-sm" required>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email address" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg text-sm" required>
        <input type="url" placeholder="Website URL" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg text-sm" required>
        <button type="submit" class="cta-primary w-full justify-center">Get My Free Audit &rarr;</button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted text-center mt-4">No commitment. No spam. 1,400+ UK businesses audited.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">
      <span>1,400+ audited</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>6 AI platforms</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Companies House verified</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">Rank4AI Ltd · Company 16584507 · <a href="/" class="underline">rank4ai.co.uk</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
